{"tid":1063790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[崖山以後無中華]毋忘崖山！毋忘甚麼？","createTime":"2019-03-16T04:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T08:44:17.000Z","uid":225098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8f4606d24d69b556f59666460caa630b4038c7f9","tid":1063790,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:52:55.000Z","msg":"我們不要忘記大宋人當年的徬徨。大宋人當年淪為亞細亞的孤兒，被腐敗的賈似道政府遺棄，不情不願的被逼等待著年蒙元韃虜政權殖民。然後在那一天，大宋人在釣魚城，看到那未來的宗主是個麻木不仁的屠夫政權。徬徨，是因為我們未能自立自主。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/06/02/world/TIANANMEN/TIANANMEN-master1050.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2014%2F06%2F02%2Fworld%2FTIANANMEN%2FTIANANMEN-master1050.jpg&h=fc5792a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們不要忘記大宋人當天的屈辱。四等人、老灶爺、嫁女送保長，韃虜將江南拿到手，就不斷罔顧大宋人的意願。金國的滅亡，從來都不是雪恥，而是災難。蒙元的本質，乃是抱著天朝心態的黨國主義帝國，一開始就要將大宋收歸為服務權貴的蒙古殖民地。未來的宗主太霸道，被遺棄的大宋子民苦無出路。是以當中原出現了爭取驅逐韃虜、恢復中華的運動，大宋人就將所有的希望，寄託於中原的群雄身上。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.ntdtv.com/pic/2018/6-2/p8874831a399244816.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.ntdtv.com%2Fpic%2F2018%2F6-2%2Fp8874831a399244816.jpg&h=7dcfad08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不敢想起，未敢忘記，但我們真的毋忘崖山？如果我們看不到大一統蒙古國族主義對自由、對個體的摧殘，如果我們看不到唯有自立、自主、自決方能使漢地迎向自由文明，那樣我們其實就未有從歷史中學到教訓，如此其實也是以另一種方式替崖山回憶劃上句號。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Candlelight_vigil_for_the_26th_anniversary_of_the_June_4th_incident_in_Victoria_Park2C_Hong_Kong_hMgfc_1200x0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FCandlelight_vigil_for_the_26th_anniversary_of_the_June_4th_incident_in_Victoria_Park2C_Hong_Kong_hMgfc_1200x0.JPG&h=4d4f6917&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9069988ab3fd7b87d16845a31f9e869964093803","tid":1063790,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7cb1292c1ef12c98c44ab6b146112c4c35fd03","tid":1063790,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66dbe01d8d1d3b8b1c9316ee48044f19e99a4a8b","tid":1063790,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14dab45e68b260af8e82b2825e6ced19240e213","tid":1063790,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba940fcb841b7f62ad38eb7b3ffbf39fad9d86d2","tid":1063790,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d14dab45e68b260af8e82b2825e6ced19240e213","tid":1063790,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:57:10.000Z","msg":"金人？中國人咪金人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1918ef40177fb858846b176e7c83e62e273f9e72","tid":1063790,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"參與八九民運的人講的是滿洲狗的語言，爭的是滿洲狗的民主，關我撚事？<br />\n只有廣東話一眾南方語系先係中華正統。"},{"pid":"22690d32feccab8588f10df0637e232535a2de98","tid":1063790,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d14dab45e68b260af8e82b2825e6ced19240e213","tid":1063790,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T05:41:15.000Z","msg":"我愛叫雞，我愛中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903b1fbf460c5bab11d86cd734730781dd6e35b2","tid":1063790,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"貧憎，老納兩位大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1536d1502706259e4f60032f591be5861f9dc11d","tid":1063790,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T05:51:09.000Z","msg":"宋代先係漢文化既巔峰，人地個皇帝都知道制衡，設個丞相出黎制衡自己權力，不殺士大夫真係貫徹始終，話唔殺讀書人真係就唔殺最多放逐。以前既皇帝未死就開始修墓勞民修財好大喜功，但宋代既皇陵係最唔顯眼，好多到而家都搵唔到，因為宋朝皇帝規定要自己死後先可以修墓，而且限制180日內就要修好，呢D咪就節儉囉。宋之後到而家都冇一個朝代比得上。"},{"pid":"c94410902a8be41c409c0fde516a90d3cd38f6cf","tid":1063790,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1536d1502706259e4f60032f591be5861f9dc11d","tid":1063790,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T05:51:09.000Z","msg":"宋代先係漢文化既巔峰，人地個皇帝都知道制衡，設個丞相出黎制衡自己權力，不殺士大夫真係貫徹始終，話唔殺讀書人真係就唔殺最多放逐。以前既皇帝未死就開始修墓勞民修財好大喜功，但宋代既皇陵係最唔顯眼，好多到而家都搵唔到，因為宋朝皇帝規定要自己死後先可以修墓，而且限制180日內就要修好，呢D咪就節儉囉。宋之後到而家都冇一個朝代比得上。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be35ba762d49f1584a701ceab426d003cd87908e","tid":1063790,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34fc3a3a3d69f7fa07c39c86ffa651e3d72f6445","tid":1063790,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}